###----------------------------------------------------------------------------
###                     Pruebas para Comercios
###----------------------------------------------------------------------------

### Crear Comercio
POST http://localhost:3000/api/admin/comercios
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "nombre": "Comercio 6",
  "CIF": "CIF0006",
  "direccion": "Calle 6",
  "email": "comercio6@example.com",
  "telefono": "6677889911"
}

### Consultar Todos los Comercios
GET http://localhost:3000/api/admin/comercios
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Consultar Comercio por ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/admin/comercios/665e547ac5f6a9059d069659
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Actualizar Comercio
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/admin/comercios/665786cdc663c63590307de7
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "nombre": "Super Comercio 1",
  "direccion": "Calle Verdadera 456"
}

### Borrar Comercio 
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/admin/comercios/666041e0b9bc68d084386bd7
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###----------------------------------------------------------------------------
###               Pruebas para usuarios Registrados
###----------------------------------------------------------------------------

### Obtener todos los usuarios registrados
GET http://localhost:3000/api/admin/users
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Obtener un usuarios registrados en especifico
GET http://localhost:3000/api/admin/user/665fbef2560e494814e15cf8
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Actualizar un usuario
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/admin/user/6661376ca0880e5f860fc6ae
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "nombre" : "nuevoNombre",
  "email" : "nuevoEmail@gmail.com"
}

### Actualizar la contraseña de un usuario
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/admin/user/6661376ca0880e5f860fc6ae/password
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "newPassword" : "nuevaContraseñaAunMasSegura"
}

### Actualizar el correo electronico de un usuario
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/admin/user/6661376ca0880e5f860fc6ae/email
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "newEmail" : "nueviiiiiiiiiiiisimoEmail@gmail.com"
}

### Obtener un usuarios registrados en especifico
DELETE  http://localhost:3000/api/admin/user/6661445c482ddd2c5011b490
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}